they are land less labourers, they collect seasonal forest products like kendu leaf,
straw, Mohulo flower (in Odia language) etc. Their main cultivation is ragi, paddy,
maize and dal seeds. Sometimes the two eldest sons assist their parents in cultivation
work. In addition to that they go for daily labour. To help the parents and give Biliam
a chance to have a better future, he was admitted into the program.

income. The parents of the child were approached and the child has been admitted v
